    <%- include('partials/nav') %> <div class="privacy-container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: May 2026</p>
      
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>Welcome to Taskify. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy will inform you as to how we look after your personal data when you visit our website.</p>
      
